s and suppliers competitive positioning history culture and all other aspects of its operations in addition mr simon possesses a great depth of knowledge and experience regarding the organic and natural products industry on a global basis not easily found elsewhere he is considered to be a prominent visionary and leader in the organic and natural products industry in addition mr simons prior employment experience and other directorships bring him valuable insight into the broader consumer packaged goods industry source the hain celestial group inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view irwin d simons full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like irwin d simon more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in irwin d simons network and community follow changes in irwin d simons employment and moneyinmotion connect with irwin d simon through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example irwin d simon irwin d simons connections  sign up now to view irwin d simons  connections » adam m aron dir chief executive officer and president amc entertainment holdings inc joseph jimenez board member general motors company anne marie odonovan board member indigo books  music inc william p lauder executive chairman the estée lauder companies inc daniel r glickman former lead independent director cme group inc d edward i smyth former senior vice president  chief administrative officer heinz h j miles s nadal former chairman chief executive officer and president mdc partners inc raymond w kelly former board member the hain celestial group inc ros lesperance board member newell brands ian g ashken board member newell brands popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r mu